\id TIT - SYN- Siyin Bible 
\ide 65001 - Unicode (UTF-8)
\h TAITUS 
\toc1 TITUS 
\toc2 Taitus 
\toc3 Tit 
\mt1 TITUS  
\mt2 Titus  
\c 1  
\s1 Paupuina  
\p
\v 1 Paul, Pathian i tealna te upna bang in, Pathianmi hina zui in thuman a lungkimpui Pathian i sal le Jesus Christ i sawltak;   
\p
\v 2 Tawntung nuntakna i lametna sungah, leilot thu son ngawl Pathian in leitung kipatcil ma in a kamciam sa;   
\p
\v 3 A hun a cin ciang in Ama thu sia thuhilna tungtawn in hong kilang a, eite hong tan Pathian i thupiakna bang in keima tungah hong ap hi;   
\p
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt 2 Cor 8:23; Gal 2:3; 2Tim 4:10.\x*Upna kibang sungah ka tapa tatak Titus tungah Pa Pathian le eite hong tan Topa Jesus Christ tung pan thuthiamna, hesuakna le thinnopna hong om tahen.   
\s1 Pastor  
\p
\v 5 Keima i kong sawlsa bang in, a kisam nate a pua tu le khuapi tatuam ah upa te nasep pia tu in, Crete ah nangma kong nusia hi:   
\p
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt 1 Tim 3:2-7\x*Paubang ngawl, zi khat nei, cilesa deina sangah mawsiat tu om ngawl le thu ni ngawl tate hi ngawl in, a thuman ta nei te ahile upa nasep pia in.   
\p
\v 7 Banghangziam cile bishop\f + \fr 1:7 \fq bishop \ft pawlpi keam sya\f* sia Pathian neisa keam te bang in paubang ngawl hi tu a, ama thu bek dei, a thin tom, sapittui dawn nuam mama, ngual vua thei le a thiangtho ngawl sum le pai duhop te hi heak tahen;   
\p
\v 8 Ahihang leangna a it, mipha te a it, mi pilvang, mi thutang, mithiangtho, a ki tek zo mi hi tahen;   
\p
\v 9 Hilna man a hanthawn thei hi tu le, ngual thu nial thei te a zo thei natu in, a muanhuai hilna thu sia a khotak in a len hi tahen.   
\p
\v 10 Banghangziam cile thu ni nuam ngawl, a mannung ngawl kampau le ngual a theam tam mama om hi, a tuan in vunteap tan te sungah tam mama hi:   
\p
\v 11 Amate kam humsak tu a hihi, a thiangtho ngawl sum le pai duhopna hang in, a hil kul ngawl te zong hil uh a, innkuan sung theampo lumlet siat hi.   
\p
\v 12 Amate sung pan khat, amate kamsang khat in, Crete mite sia leilot thuson te, nganhing ngilo te, datham antuang te, ci hi.   
\p
\v 13 Hi te sia a man a hihi. Tua ahikom upna a man heak natu in nasiatak in tei in;   
\p
\v 14 Judah te phuatawm tangthu te le, mihing te thupiakna te sia thuman pan pialsak ahi hu in thusim heak hi.   
\p
\v 15 A thiangtho te kungah na theampo thiangtho hi: ahihang a thiangtho ngawl te le a um ngawl te tungah bangma thiangtho ngawl hi; amate i ngaisutna khentel theina zong thiangtho ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 16 Amate in Pathian ka he uh hi, ci in pualak uh hi; ahihang amate in a sepna uh taw Pathian nial uh a, a lipkhaphuai te, thu ni ngawl te le ngamtat phatbna ah ngina ngawl uh hi.   
\c 2  
\s1 Hilna Maan  
\p
\v 1 Ahihang nang na hile, hilna maan taw a kisi thu te hil in:   
\p
\v 2 Tabang in pasal khangham te sia a pilvang, a zatak huai, ki tekna nei, upna maan, itna le thuakzawkna nei te hi tahen.   
\p
\v 3 Tasia bangma in, nupi khangham te zong, thianthona taw a kisi ngamtatna taw nungta tahen, a maan ngawl ngual mawsiat nate le sapittui tampi a zang te hi heak tahen, na pha hil te hi tahen;   
\p
\v 4 Tabang in nupi khangmoi te a pilvang tu, a pasal te le a tate a it tu,   
\p
\v 5 Thinsung thupi, thinsung thiangtho, innkuan keamcing te, mi pha, pasal te thu ni te hi tu in hil tu a, tabang in Pathian thu sia sonsiat hi ngawl tu hi.   
\p
\v 6 Tabangma in a khangmoi pasal te zong a pilvang tu in hanthawn in.   
\p
\v 7 Na theampo ah a ettetak in ngamtat pha te nangma tatak in lak in: hilna taw kisai ki hilna phangawl kihel ngawl, a zatak huai le deisakna te kilangsak in,   
\p
\v 8 Ngual i hong mawsiat thei ngawl natu in na kampau nate man tahen; tabang in na thu a phangawl in a son tu uh nei ngawl in, hong langpan te a maizum tu uh hi.   
\p
\v 9 Sila te in amate i to te thu ni tu, na theampo ah lungkimsak mama tu le kam zo kik ngawl tu;   
\p
\v 10 Na ngu ku ngawl tu, muantak a hina theampo taw eite nuntakna hong ngum Pathian i hilna sia kilangsak tu in hanthawn in.   
\p
\v 11 Banghangziam cile ngupna hong paipui Pathian i thuthiamna sia mi theampo tungah kilang zo hi,   
\p
\v 12 Tua Pathian i thuthiamna in Pathian nei ngawl nuntakzia le cilesa deina nial tu a, a pilvang, a thutang, Pathianmi hina taw tu hun sungah a nungta tu in hong hil hi;   
\p
\v 13 A lian Pathian le eite hong ngum Jesus Christ vangliantak in a kilang natu a thupha lametna masuan tu hi;   
\p
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Ps 130:8; \xt Ex 19:5; Thuhlkk 4:20; 7:6; 14:2; 1Pet 2:9.\x*Eite atu in Ama le Ama a kipiakna sia, phat ngawlna theampo pan hong tan tu a, Ama kungah a tuanngen minam a hi tu le nasep pha te atu in a thalawp te a hi tu in hong thiangthosak hi.   
\p
\v 15 Hi thu theampo sia thuneina theampo taw hanthawn in a, tei in. Kuama in nang hong thusimngawl heak tahen.   
\c 3  
\s1 Tapidaw Nuntakna  
\p
\v 1 Ngam uk te le thunei te thu nit natu a hizong, thukhenmang te thu mang tu in a hizong, nasep pha peuma seam tu kinging sa in om tu a hizong,   
\p
\v 2 Ngual sonsia ngawl, ngual taw thu ki nial in buai ngawl tu, thinsau le ngual theampo tungah nunneam na kilangsak tu in phawksak kik in.   
\p
\v 3 Banghangziam cile eite tatak zong nidang lai in a mawmaw, thu ni ngawl, theamna thuak, cilesa deina le lungkimna a tatuam te a seam te, ngualdang tungah deisakna phangawl le hazatna nei te, a ngaimawk huai le khat le khat a ki ensan te i hihi.   
\p
\v 4 Ahihang tua zawkciang in eite hong ngum Pathian i phatna le itna sia mihing tungah hong kilang a,   
\p
\v 5 I sepna sa thutang suana nasep te hang hi ngawl in, Ama hesuakna bang in hong suathaksakna taw sawp thiangthona le Thaa Thiangtho i thaksua na taw hong tan hi;   
\p
\v 6 Eite hong tan Jesus Christ tungtawn in tua Thaa Thiangtho sia i tungah a dimlet in hong buaksuk hi;   
\p
\v 7 I lamet tawntung nuntakna bangma in, ngamhlua te i hi thei natu in, Ama thuthiamna tungtawn in thutang hong suaksak hi.   
\p
\v 8 Hi thu sia a thuman kammal a hihi, Pathian a umte in ngamtat pha te a seam tawntung tu in kidawm tahen, ci thu te sia a tawntung thupitak in na hil tu ka dei hi. Hi thu te sia mihing te atu pha in, phattuamna om hi.   
\p
\v 9 Ahihang a mawmawt huai thudokna te le pu le pa khang thu te, ki hauna te, thukham hang in ki nialna te pial in; banghangziam cile hi te sia phattuamna nei ngawl a luithathong a hihi.   
\p
\v 10 Pawl a khen mihing khat sia a khatveina le a ni veina thu na hil zawkciang in sang nawn heak in;   
\p
\v 11 Tua pa sia ama le ama mawsiat thuak tu in mawna vawt a, paikhial hi, ci na he hi.   
\s1 A Khakbel Vaithakna  
\p
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt Sawl 20:4; Eph 6:21,22; Col 4:7,8; 2Tim 4:12.\x*Artemas a hibale Tychicus, na kungah kong paisak ciang in, keima kung Nicopolis ah pai tu in hong hanciam tan; banghangziam cile tua mun ah phalbi sung om tu in ka khensat hi.   
\p
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Sawl 18:24; 1 Cor 16:12\x*Sitnipa Zenas le Apollos te sia amate khualhawna mun ah hanciam in hawpui in a, amate tungah bangma kisapna omsak heak in.   
\p
\v 14 Taciang i mihing te zong nga nei ngawl te a hi ngawl natu le a kisam na mun ah zak tu in nasep pha te zomsuak tu in statsat ngawl in sin ta hen.   
\p
\v 15 Ka kung a omte theampo in hong paupui hi. Upna sungah hong itte paupui in. Note theampo tungah thuthiamna hong om tahen. Amen.   